Class GameLevel

java.lang.Object
city.cs.engine.World
game.GameLevel
Direct Known Subclasses:
Level1, Level2, Level3, Level4
public abstract class GameLevel extends city.cs.engine.World
The base class for all the game levels.

Each level extends this class and provides its own implementation for level completion, background image, and level name.
